        <h2>We Are A Voice For Those Who Have None</h2></center><br>
        <p class="col-md-6 wow bounceInUp">

PetVerify.org was established in North America and is, today, the only online pet owner verification system in the world that utilizes AIP℗, a patented artificial intelligence that evaluates the history and qualifications of individuals wanting to become pet owners.
</p>
