        <h2>The PetVerify™ Process</h2></center><br>
        <p class="col-md-6">

At Pet Verify™, we wanted to help minimize the waiting period associated with adopting a pet.  Our patent pending technology allows you or your potential customer to complete a universal online application, scan various critical elements of the customer (background, credit, terrorist watch list and/or social media) and transfer all of that information into a PDF that can be downloaded or emailed to you and/or your client to process an adoption.
</p>
      <p class="col-md-6">
        By using this system, potential owners can be united with their new companions faster than ever before.<br>
<br>
